name: Charles Astor Window Blinds
tag_list: window, blinds, roller-blinds, vertical, roller, venetian, roman, pleated, panel, shading, shades
overview:
Charles Astor window blinds will enhance the decor in any room in the home or office. With a huge range of colours and fabrics from which to choose, you can be assured that your new window blinds can offer more than just privacy and protection, they can bring additional style to any interior design scheme.

In addition to their fabulous visual impact, many of our blinds offer significant additional benefits that might not always immediately apparent.

Many of our fabrics provide exceptional performance that is proven to reduce heat in summer and retain heat in winter to save you money.

Roller blinds, roman, vertical and venetian blinds available online.
